<p><span class="h2">L.S.,</span></p>
<p><span class="h2">Forgive me for doubting you. Your recruitment of <a href="/hopping-through-worlds">Agent Hopper</a> has been a great boon to the Library and ourselves. And it's thanks in no small part to their unique talent, variable as it is.</span></p>
<p><span class="h2">Their continued findings in this <a href="/broken-masquerade-hub">unmasqued branch</a> of The Tree have been very eye-opening. I've taken the liberty of compiling them in one of our extra-universal documentation indices, attached below.</span></p>
